inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
union requests,pageViews,customEvents
| where timestamp > ago(1d)
| where tostring(customDimensions["UserAgent"]) startswith "AzurePowerShell/Az"
| summarize Occurences=count() by Command=tostring(customDimensions["Command"])
| join kind=fullouter (union requests,pageViews,customEvents
| where timestamp > ago(1d)
| where tostring(customDimensions["UserAgent"]) startswith "AzurePowerShell/Az"
| where tostring(customDimensions["IsSuccess"]) == "False"
| summarize Failures=count() by Command=tostring(customDimensions["Command"])) on Command
| extend Successes = toint(Occurences) - toint(Failures) 
| extend SuccessRate=toreal(Successes)/toreal(Occurences)
| where  SuccessRate < 0.9 and toint(Occurences) > 100
| order by SuccessRate asc, Occurences desc

| where tostring(customDimensions["IsSuccess"]) == "False"
| summarize Failures=count() by Command=tostring(customDimensions["Command"])) on Command

| order by SuccessRate asc, Occurences desc

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
union requests,pageViews,customEvents
| where timestamp > ago(1d)
| where (customDimensions["UserAgent"] contains "AzurePowershell/az")
| summarize Successes=count() by Command=tostring(customDimensions["Command"]), Outcome=tostring(customDimensions["IsSuccess"])
| where (Outcome == "True")
| join (union requests,pageViews,customEvents
| where timestamp > ago(1d)
| where (customDimensions["UserAgent"] contains "AzurePowershell/az")
| summarize Failures=count() by Command=tostring(customDimensions["Command"]), Outcome=tostring(customDimensions["IsSuccess"])
| where (Outcome == "False")) on Command
| where Failures > Successes and Failures > 50
| project Command, Successes, Failures
| order by Failures desc
